{"pid":"84af6ed478ca43c15056a918ffc0310a47725ab3","tid":213493,"uid":79627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:46:30.000Z","msg":"飲開有奶+糖<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n飲過一次齋啡乜都冇之後返唔到轉頭，慢慢&rdquo;㗳&ldquo;陣咖啡味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後飲返咩咖啡都覺得糖水咁"},{"pid":"c00165fdac9a0845b3ef9bbd234f70ca72121ef3","tid":213493,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>次次飲d朋友都話<br />\n唔會好苦咩?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> +1<br />\n<br />\n就係想飲佢呢陣味<br />\n唔係點解要飲齋啡</blockquote><br />\n其實真正好飲既咖啡係甘而不苦<br />\n有啲仲會有果酸，果仁既味道"},{"pid":"a3f4047264e341ab4266cf87cd50bf1845325c80","tid":213493,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次飲d朋友都話<br />\n唔會好苦咩?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> +1<br />\n<br />\n就係想飲佢呢陣味<br />\n唔係點解要飲齋啡</blockquote><br />\n其實真正好飲既咖啡係甘而不苦<br />\n有啲仲會有果酸，果仁既味道</blockquote><br />\n飲過好野真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d59beabc0d0155eb4a723c612615255fa68483e5","tid":213493,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:30:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>次次飲d朋友都話<br />\n唔會好苦咩?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> +1<br />\n<br />\n就係想飲佢呢陣味<br />\n唔係點解要飲齋啡</blockquote><br />\n其實真正好飲既咖啡係甘而不苦<br />\n有啲仲會有果酸，果仁既味道</blockquote><br />\n飲過好野真係返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係<br />\n飲過好野之後再無一次係 Starbucks 飲過啡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d81128929c5a00241c2665a5a480a87a4562e9","tid":213493,"uid":60047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T06:46:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>涷齋啡先爽</blockquote><br />\n要走甜<br />\n唔係佢一定會糖水</blockquote><br />\n所以每次食飯都好谷氣<br />\n話明齋啡，就梗係乜都冇<br />\n點解會加左糖漿<br />\n加在糖漿就已經唔係齋啡啦<br />\n<br />\n明明記得以前凍齋啡係唔甜的"},{"pid":"0e2b2ef4759729a51eec6f44cee14a58427b69fe","tid":213493,"uid":77277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:03:34.000Z","msg":"飲開Black Coffe<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03903b1cea1b3d59ef651148c679e1ef876a23e3","tid":213493,"uid":63190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"市面上有冇齋啡買，便利店唔覺有<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1d14ec05ff9789db156ac89c19fa3704ed0d02e","tid":213493,"uid":59181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"飲熱就齋啡 飲凍就檸啡走甜<br />\n<br />\n有冇同好？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b206118d3b3fdcfb381638f25f36c2671f2b0a0","tid":213493,"uid":5762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T08:26:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>市面上有冇齋啡買，便利店唔覺有<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n某啲7仔 OK 會有UCC齋啡<br />\n日本就間間都有 仲大把選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b031909d46306225bc50269619fb325c50f1fa","tid":213493,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T02:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}